---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Blog
description: Shorter cadence — notes, updates, things we built recently.
permalink: /blog/
---

<div class="container">
  <h1>Blog</h1>
  <p class="muted">Shorter posts: things we built, what we're thinking about, updates from the firm.</p>

  {% if collections.blog.length > 0 %}
    <ul class="post-list">
      {% for post in collections.blog %}
        <li>
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">
            <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
            <p class="muted small">{{ post.date | date }}</p>
            {% if post.data.summary %}<p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  {% else %}
    <p class="muted">No posts published yet.</p>
  {% endif %}
</div>
